item.title: CVE-2024-28099|2024-04-15T10:31:34.198Z -- keyence%20corporation -- vt%20studio
item.description: VT STUDIO Ver.8.32 and earlier contains an issue with the DLL search path, which may lead to insecurely loading Dynamic Link Libraries. As a result, arbitrary code may be executed with the privileges of the running application.
